## Architecture

This agent implements the 8-stage message pipeline:

```
channel → queue → classifier → memory → SDK → exfil guard → cost footer → reply
```

…with the four-ring security model: allowlist → PIN → exfil guard → audit log, plus a kill-phrase short-circuit that bypasses the allowlist.

