## Operations

- **Hive mind:** task records land in `~/.agents/hive.db`. Query with any SQLite client.
- **Audit log:** `~/.agents/audit/{{name}}.jsonl`, one JSON object per line.
- **Kill phrase:** send `emergency stop` (or whatever you set `AGENT_KILL_PHRASE` to). Locks all sessions immediately.

## When things go wrong

| Symptom | Likely cause |
|---|---|
| Bot ignores your messages | Your chat/user ID isn't in the allowlist env var. Check rings 1 & 2 logs. |
| "Wrong PIN" no matter what | `AGENT_PIN` in `.env` doesn't match what you typed. PINs are exact-string. |
| `[REDACTED — exfil guard]` in legitimate output | A pattern in `EXFIL_DENY_PATTERNS` is too broad. Tune it. |
| Hybrid call gets 401 from managed peer | `BRIDGE_HMAC_SECRET` doesn't match between local and managed sides. |
| Managed registration 400s on MCP | One of your MCP URLs isn't HTTPS-reachable, or it's a STDIO server. |
| Deploy fails: `Permission denied (publickey)` | Remote host doesn't have your pubkey. Run `ssh-copy-id <user>@<host>` first. |
